  "summary": "VLCC\nLimited enquiry in the ME Gulf saw rates ease three points with Unipec taking ‘Leonidas' at WS 54.5 for China, while Formosa paid WS 52 to Taiwan all basis 270,000mt and the market remains under downward pressure. For US Gulf discharge, rates for 280,000mt also fell to around WS 21.5 Cape/Cape. In West Africa, Unipec fixed 260,000mt to China at around WS 53.5 down 1.5 points with potential for further softening.",
